<TiTle>Technology Assessment Advisory Council</TiTle>
<H1>Technology Assessment Advisory Council</H1>
<HR>
<P>The Technology Assessment Advisory Council (TAAC) was established by OTA's statute, and members are appointed by OTA's Congressional Technology Assessment Board (TAB).  The Council advises TAB and the Director on issues and other matters related to science, technology, and technology assessment.
<HR>
<PRE>
