<TITLE>OTA Technology Assessment Board</TITLE>
<H1>Technology Assessment Board of the 104th Congress</H1>
<strong>The Technology Assessment Board (TAB) Chairman for the 104th Congress will 
be the ranking House Republican; the Vice Chair will be the ranking Senate 
Democrat.</strong>   <i>(Awaiting appointment by the House and Senate Leadership)</i>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
<BR>
