<TR><TD COLSPAN=100>3) nausea</TD>
<TD COLSPAN=80></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=20><center>True</TD><TD>&#015;</TD></center>
<TD COLSPAN=5></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=20><center>False</TD><TD>&#015;</TD></TR></center>

<TR><TD COLSPAN=100>4) neck stiffness</TD>
<TD COLSPAN=80></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=20><center>True</TD><TD>&#015;</TD></center>
<TD COLSPAN=5></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=20><center>False</TD><TD>&#015;</TD></TR></center>

<TD></TD><TR>
<TD COLSPAN=150>
G) Determine which one of the following statements is false. The following commonly induce headache:

<TR><TD COLSPAN=100>1) trigeminal neuralgia</TD>
