<DOCHDR>
http://www.dotpharmacy.co.uk:80/upcanna.html 194.72.154.151 19970124082133 text/html 13872
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 08:21:31 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
