<TD COLSPAN=30></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=20><center>True</TD><TD>&#015;</TD></center>
<TD COLSPAN=5></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=20><center>False</TD><TD>&#015;</TD></TR></center>


<TD COLSPAN=150>
G)  Identify which one of the following statements about drugs used for treating eating disorders is false:</TD>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=110>1)  drug absorption is impaired</TD>
