<DOCNO>WT16-B26-112</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA077-000515-B035-356</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.dotpharmacy.co.uk:80/uphalluc.html 194.72.154.151 19970124082524 text/html 14543
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 08:25:22 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
