<P>
<H1 align=center><B>Pick of the Week</B></H1>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the December 7, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>
<P>

<A HREF="#a">PSNI seeks 2020 vision</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#b">Third primary care White Paper on the way?</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#c">Fees concern in Scotland</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#d">PSNC settles the details for 1996</A>
