<P>
<H1 align=center><B>Pick of the Week</B></H1>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the July 20, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>
<P>
<A HREF="#a">3000 pharmacies could go if RPM is lost...</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#b">...survey reveals the threats</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#c">Pharmacists to be more clinical with methadone?</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#d">No sign of Commons Pharmacy Group</A>
<P>
