<H1 align=center><B>Pick of the Week</B></H1>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the August 17, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>
<P>
<A HREF="#a">RPSGB may guide on PMR sales</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#b">Nottingham GP asks for judicial review</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#c">Northern Ireland publishes health strategy for next century</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#d">Health of the Nation targets missed</A>
