<H1 align=center><B>Pick of the Week</B></H1>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the November 16, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>
<P>
<A HREF="#a">Pharmacists to be involved in ADR reporting from April</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#b">Rural disputes at High Court</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#c">New ways to record private prescriptions</A>
