<H1 align=center><B>Pick of the Week</B></H1>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the August 10, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>
<P>
<A HREF="#a">Dietary supplements category proposed</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#b">No pay deal yet for England and Wales</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#c">CPP plans changes to membership rules</A>
<P>
<A HREF="#d">Restriction on terfenadine</A>
