<H1 align=center><B>Pick of the Week</B></H1>

<P>
<P align=center><I>Top stories from the March 30, 1996, issue of Chemist &amp; Druggist
Newsweekly</I></P>
<P>
<A HREF="#a">Pharmacy Healthcare Scheme's future secure</A>
